**Multi-System Storage Architecture:**
```yaml
# Test Strategy Report
filename: Knowledge/testing/test_strategy_$(date +%Y-%m-%d_%H-%M-%S).md
frontmatter:
  type: test_strategy
  timestamp: $(date -Iseconds)
  classification: testing_intelligence
  ml_labels: [test_coverage, strategy_effectiveness, quality_improvement]
  success_metrics: [coverage_percentage, defect_detection_rate, test_efficiency]
